{{Documentation|doc=
This is a [[Template:Navbar|navbar]] used at the top of modding pages to assist with user navigation. A navbar differs from a [[Template:Navbox|navbox]] in that it is intended to link to broad overview pages rather than being an exhaustive list of objects.

== Usage ==
